These yummy and flavourful banana, walnut and maple muffins are super easy to bake, and can be recreated in under 30 minutes. The maple added to this recipe gives the muffins a sweet and delectable taste for the health bunnies who still battle with the occasional sweet tooth. Try out these delicious banana, walnut and maple muffins to be enjoyed over breakfast or as an any time of the day snack for the next couple of days. Double your ingredients to create a larger batch of these scrumptious muffins which you could share with your loved ones. ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Avocado chicken parmigiana This recipe was found on delicious.com.au